/span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-brand-50 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-brand-700\">软件开发</span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-brand-50 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-brand-700\">本科</span></div></header><section class=\"mb-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\"><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900\">偏好评估</h2><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"w-24 shrink-0 text-sm text-gray-600\">兴趣匹配</span><div class=\"h-2 flex-1 overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-gray-200\"><div class=\"h-full rounded-full transition-all bg-emerald-500\" style=\"width:85%\"></div></div><span class=\"w-10 text-right text-sm font-medium text-gray-800\">85</span></div><p class=\"mt-0.5 pl-28 text-xs text-gray-400\">与该路径所需技能和日常工作的兴趣契合度</p></div><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"w-24 shrink-0 text-sm text-gray-600\">时间弹性</span><div class=\"h-2 flex-1 overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-gray-200\"><div class=\"h-full rounded-full transition-all bg-emerald-500\" style=\"width:80%\"></div></div><span class=\"w-10 text-right text-sm font-medium text-gray-800\">80</span></div><p class=\"mt-0.5 pl-28 text-xs text-gray-400\">路径对时间安排的自由度与灵活度</p></div><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"w-24 shrink-0 text-sm text-gray-600\">生活方式兼容</span><div class=\"h-2 flex-1 overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-gray-200\"><div class=\"h-full rounded-full transition-all bg-emerald-500\" style=\"width:75%\"></div></div><span class=\"w-10 text-right text-sm font-medium text-gray-800\">75</span></div><p class=\"mt-0.5 pl-28 text-xs text-gray-400\">路径与目标生活方式的适配程度</p></div><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"w-24 shrink-0 text-sm text-gray-600\">成长曲线</span><div class=\"h-2 flex-1 overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-gray-200\"><div class=\"h-full rounded-full transition-all bg-amber-500\" style=\"width:60%\"></div></div><span class=\"w-10 text-right text-sm font-medium text-gray-800\">60</span></div><p class=\"mt-0.5 pl-28 text-xs text-gray-400\">路径的长期发展与上升空间</p></div></div></section><section class=\"mb-8\"><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900\">硬约束评估</h2><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border p-3 border-gray-200 bg-white\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span>✅</span><h4 class=\"font-medium text-gray-900\">经济可行性</h4></div><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600\">零额外投入，毕业即可获得收入。起薪 12-15k 在上海可覆盖基本生活。</p></div></div></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border p-3 border-gray-200 bg-white\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span>✅</span><h4 class=\"font-medium text-gray-900\">语言能力</h4></div><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600\">外企需要基本英语读写能力（CET-4/6），日常沟通以中文为主。</p></div></div></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border p-3 border-gray-200 bg-white\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span>✅</span><h4 class=\"font-medium text-gray-900\">学历准入</h4></div><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600\">外企和中型公司对双非学历的接受度较高，更看重技术面试表现。大厂（阿里/腾讯/字节）则较难进入。</p></div></div></di",
